    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place" rend="right">Camden<ptr target="nyp.00411_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1878-09-01">Sunday Sept 1 5 p m</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>

            <p>Still keep real well &#38; hearty considering&#8212;Anticipate visiting Wash[ington] sometime this winter&#8212;Saw your friend Ch: Johnson<ptr target="nyp.00411_n2"/> a few evenings since on the ferry&#8212;had quite a talk about you, &#38;c&#8212;</p>
            
            <p>Nothing very new in my affairs&#8212;(nothing to complain of)&#8212;Very hot here to-day&#8212;bad for yellow fever if prevalent, &#38; continuous&#8212;</p>

            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">W W</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
